column2: "Hey! Hey, partner! Why are you spacing out?"
"Nah, I get it. It's our last exam mission, so you're nervous, right? Well, me too."
"We should be a little on edge. But as long as we do our best, it'll turn out okay, partner."
"Hey, partner. We're still pretty new, but let's at least try to get the basics down."
"Ah! Hey, partner! Wait up, don't leave me behind!"
